### List all available metric names
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics

### JVM heap memory used
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics/jvm.memory.used?tag=area:heap

### Total HTTP server requests served
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics/http.server.requests

### HTTP requests filtered by outcome
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics/http.server.requests?tag=outcome:SUCCESS
